@startuml embedder
!include ../_includes/style.iuml
!include ../_includes/actors.iuml

title Embedder — dual mode: server (interactive) + CLI (bulk)

package "src/main/modelhub/" {
  component "embedderLifecycle.ts\n• ensureEmbedderReady(filePath)\n• in-flight launch promise\n  (concurrency-safe)\n• stopManagedEmbedders()" as EMBED_LC
  component "embedderCli.ts\n(2026-05-23)\n• embedViaLlamaCli(opts)\n  spawn → JSON → exit\n• resolveEmbedderCliFn()\n  derives llama-embedding\n  from llama-server runner\n• deriveLlamaEmbeddingPath" as EMBED_CLI
  component "launchModelByPath\n(via launch.ts)\nlaunchedBy: 'embedder'\ncustomArgs: '--embedding'" as LAUNCH
  component "EmbedClient\n(routing/embed.ts)\nHTTP POST /v1/embeddings" as EMBED_CLIENT
  component "routingConfig.ts\n.routingEmbedderPath /\n.routingEmbedderBaseUrl" as RC
}

component "characterizeAll\n(bulk, per-model loop)" as CHAR_ALL
component "routeByVectors\n(interactive query)" as ROUTE

CHAR_ALL --> EMBED_CLI : resolveEmbedderCliFn() once\nthen embed() per model
ROUTE --> RC : effectiveRoutingParams.embedder

RC --> EMBED_LC : kind:'managed'\n+ filePath\n(server-backed)
RC ..> EMBED_CLIENT : kind:'external'\n+ baseUrl (direct)

EMBED_LC --> LAUNCH : spawn if not running
LAUNCH --> LLAMA_EMBED : llama-server\n--embedding (port 8081)
LLAMA_EMBED --> EMBED_LC : /v1/models OK\n(ready probe, 60s timeout)
EMBED_LC --> EMBED_CLIENT : baseUrl
EMBED_CLIENT --> LLAMA_EMBED : POST /v1/embeddings

component "llama-embedding.exe\n(one-shot CLI)" as LLAMA_EMBED_CLI
EMBED_CLI ..> LLAMA_EMBED_CLI : spawn one-shot per call

note right of LLAMA_EMBED_CLI
  Sibling of llama-server in the
  same llama.cpp build folder.
  Spawned per call, prints JSON
  on stdout, exits.
end note

note bottom of EMBED_LC
  SERVER mode (interactive routing):
  resident process, low-latency queries,
  reused across calls. Idempotent + crash-
  safe (boot crash ⇒ null ⇒ R5 fallback).
end note

note bottom of EMBED_CLI
  CLI mode (bulk characterization):
  spawn → embed → exit per model.
  Zero resident RAM between models —
  test model is the only big GGUF
  loaded at any given time.
  Both modes use the SAME embedder
  GGUF (routingEmbedderPath).
end note

note right of LLAMA_EMBED
  Visible in RunningModelsPanel,
  grouped by `launchedBy: 'embedder'`,
  alongside chat models.
end note

@enduml
